{"tid":491570,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"普京宣布競逐明年俄羅斯總統","createTime":"2017-12-06T15:52:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-08T23:42:48.000Z","uid":48093,"like":172,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":77,"replies":[{"pid":"47f85109eff43c90ed57b52cd8157d5526551dd3","tid":491570,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:52:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1368751_1_L_20171206233055.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1368751_1_L_20171206233055.jpg&h=cb06df08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n俄羅斯總統普京宣布，他將參加明年舉行的總統選舉。<br />\n<br />\n他向下諾夫哥羅德市一間車廠的工人發表演說時，作出宣布。<br />\n<br />\n普京2000年起一直以總統或者總理身份掌權，若果他在明年3月的選舉勝出，將會執政至2024年。"},{"pid":"c9f265f6a2a93aafe5be1539a333f8c2962697ee","tid":491570,"uid":22858,"like":438,"dislike":5,"score":433,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i0.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/facebook/001/084/256/093.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Ffacebook%2F001%2F084%2F256%2F093.png&h=dbb5d8e8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"87f8b42ebca7c1b1b94019fa907c9331fc5c5cfa","tid":491570,"uid":36178,"like":142,"dislike":1,"score":141,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:54:23.000Z","msg":"唔選先係新聞"},{"pid":"dd97be03d531db1ea97f4f381476afb2e8fcd52b","tid":491570,"uid":76115,"like":34,"dislike":11,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T15:58:05.000Z","msg":"戰鬥民族<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 普京<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 俄羅斯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真男心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 騎老虎.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 玩筆.jpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acc11fd638ec6241923a674a51bc5bdb76be9d9e","tid":491570,"uid":55913,"lik