99e0553d770a8ed13e948b2bd527","tid":491570,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:20:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本西方價值觀夾硬套落每個國家到就唔work<br />\n好似俄羅斯,中國等等既有限度民主先係真正民主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c49286214514b90dd90593d0cdc8e6bfe3ee8511","tid":491570,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:21:06.000Z","msg":"好想知習狗會點玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf6d4e58f0e84560954debe46bd05455eb13843","tid":491570,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f0a014086f90550d03b7c3603958905478960f0","tid":491570,"uid":77143,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好想知習狗會點玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地國民教育一早洗哂腦<br />\n就算大陸一人一票選主席都係會習總贏<br />\n原因係你邊度搵個人出黎同習總鬥<br />\n其他人識你老鼠<br />\n除非李克強自立同習總鬥<br />\n結果都只會係交換職位"},{"pid":"9f526cc9dfdb8c91fef06e8a92b40eba205c389a","tid":491570,"uid":47202,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:27:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n根本西方價值觀夾硬套落每個國家到就唔work<br />\n好似俄羅斯,中國等等既有限度民主先係真正民主</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢老母細個教佢, 佢記到今日<br />\n<br />\n根本老母我見到鐘意既野就買夾硬套落每個人到就唔work<br />\n好似你老豆,呀仔你等等既有限度零用錢先係真正財務自由"},{"pid":"589b4a372f5699a4adfa57329bce8e636553f438","tid":491570,"uid":132038,"like":3,"dislike":37,"score":-34,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:27:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"52fccc481497e9e963ac443e604c595b31bfe78d","tid":491570,"uid":14103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:29:17.000Z","msg":"咩原因令佢想永遠都做總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e626f64edc58df77b644be575eae4f0b26cee632","tid":491570,"uid":38172,"like":87,"dislike":0,"score":87,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:33:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thefunnyplace.org/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/Democracy-in-Russia.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthefunnyplace.org%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F10%2FDemocracy-in-Russia.jpg&h=7d6ad70e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d4a023d63cdbfef59f8b9dbccd64fbc6ddbe4076","tid":491570,"uid":3773,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"屌點解我會睇咗做特朗普 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3eb4fea809c16249cc96b1ebe8338034f4e40df","tid":491570,"uid":38172,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:35:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://images.gawker.com/18k1daz57fwuujpg/c_fit,fl_progressive,q_80,w_636.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimages.gawker.com%2F18k1daz57fwuujpg%2Fc_fit%2Cfl_progressive%2Cq_80%2Cw_636.jpg&h=c4783995&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f1d5d4b0dec858b49b92b21d24c2e77588496406","tid":491570,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-07T05:37:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩原因令佢想永遠都做總統<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢d獨裁國家 獨裁者唯一保障<br />\n就是名義上同實際上都係最大果個.....<br />\n<br />\n到死果刻 都無人可以程序上 甚至非程序上清理自己"},{"pid":"83c54f1470e91db23f6f118c98a1ab58638b30f1","tid":491570,"uid":34666,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12